data.description: Incredible news! - Seize Your Dream Home Now! Just reduced Stunning 1.15 acre private wooded lot in an unincorporated area of Mchenry. This remarkable ranch-style home boasts river views, 3 bedrooms, a finished attic, and a partially finished basement.  Step inside to discover the brand-new 2021 wood LVP flooring and fresh lighting throughout. The kitchen is a showstopper with its white cabinets, epoxy counters, backsplash, and newer appliances. Plus, there's even a built-in bar area complete with stools! The family room or dining room offers captivating views of mature trees and the expansive private lot. Imagine soaking up the scenery from your deck or entertaining guests in the 30 x 12 attic 2nd floor bar bonus room, equipped with its own built-in bar and stools! Additional upgrades include a newer water softener, stove, AC, water heater, furnace, and roof estimated to be around 13 years. As Is/Agent related to seller. Act fast and take advantage of the countless possibilities this property offers. You can walk to nearby restaurants and shops, creating a charming and convenient lifestyle. Schedule your showing today!
